  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Double blind placebo controlled trial to evaluate whether the routine use of nasal irrigation
      with mupirocin is more effective than saline irrigations alone in reducing symptoms of
      chronic rhinosinusitis in the early postoperative period.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
